243
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:54,139
Mr. Xu Zhu, to be honest with you,

244
00:18:54,139 --> 00:18:56,040
my surname was You.

245
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:58,740
I'm a descendant of the You family, hailing from the Heroes' Gathering Manor.

246
00:19:00,320 --> 00:19:01,960
