I won't meet the ugly man.

591
00:42:04,940 --> 00:42:06,059
Hear me out.

592
00:42:06,060 --> 00:42:08,639
His Majesty wants me to go on an expedition to the south, but I'm reluctant to do so.

593
00:42:08,639 --> 00:42:11,759
I worry that if this drags on, something bad will happen.

594
00:42:13,200 --> 00:42:15,319
Since we are leaving this place,

595
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:18,959
